description.p:
In an aspect, provided herein is a method of preparing a concentrated dispersion of silver nanoparticles, comprising:
preparing a dextran solution comprising silver or silver ions;
preparing a silver precursor solution; and mixing the silver precursor solution with the dextran solution under conditions for a rapid reaction wherein the pH is above about 9 and temperature above about 40 degrees Celsius, thereby forming the concentrated dispersion of silver nanoparticles.
